Dear French Kiss Couture Community,

As the holiday season approaches, we extend our sincere gratitude for your ongoing support. We value each and every one of our customers, and we want to express our appreciation for your patience, especially during these busy times.

In the aftermath of Black Friday, we've noticed that although items are promptly dropped off, there's a delay in USPS updating order status within their system. Please be aware that once orders are handed over to the carrier, we have limited control over their processing times.

Additionally, it's important to note that the holiday season may add increased time to our shipping. We are doing our utmost to navigate these challenges and ensure that all orders are dispatched expeditiously.

To stay informed about the status of your order, we recommend providing a valid email and/or phone number during the checkout process. Order status notifications will be sent to the contact method on file. Please check your junk folders if you don't see a confirmation following placing your order.

Thank you for your continued trust and business. We appreciate your understanding as we work diligently to deliver your orders during this festive season.

Warm regards, The French Kiss Couture Team 🌟 #FrenchKissCouture #HolidayThankYou
